- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possibility as the paper mentions using feedback gains to optimize the control, which could potentially involve machine learning techniques. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a possibility as the paper deals with control of robots, which is a common application of AI. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the least likely category as the paper does not mention any use of computer vision or pattern recognition techniques.
